message.content: cs.SD, cs.SD is the most likely category as the paper deals with the evaluation of deep music representations. Other likely categories could be cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) as the paper discusses the relationship between known related points, cs.LG (Machine Learning) as the paper discusses the use of deep neural networks, cs.IR (Information Retrieval) as the paper discusses the use of feature extractors, and cs.SY (Systems and Control) as the paper proposes a systematic way to diagnose the trustworthiness of deep music representations.
